{"id":252867,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-山东律师舒向新为失地农民维权遭遇扣押/","date":"2012-09-20T03:45:56Z","modified":"2012-09-20T03:45:56Z","title":"维权网 | 山东律师舒向新为失地农民维权遭遇扣押律师证已17个月未归还","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）山东聊城市冠县去年（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年）因为无手续乱占耕地并且补偿不合理，多个村农民群体进京并且到政府门前下跪，不但问题未解决村民却被拘留。山东旭洲律师事务所律师主任舒向新律师帮助这些冠县失地农民维权，为此，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>舒向新在网上发了《县委书记洪玉振被举报》的帖子，发贴次日（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>），暴徒上门寻衅闹事，竟然扇打在场律师耳光。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>此事发生后，冠县纪委书记韩金芳带着企业老总找舒向新律师，表示他如果不代理失地农民维权案件、不发贴就给法律顾问费。舒向新律师断然拒绝，没接受收买。后来，公安局竟然以“敲诈政府”为由扣押他们律师事务所办公用品八个月。济南市司法局也以“冠县政府对舒向新投诉”</span><span>“公安局对敲诈勒索一案做出结论后才能发还律师证”为由扣押律师证，至今已</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>个月，仍不发还。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为此舒向新于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>通过济南市政府网站和济南市长信箱，向济南司法局申请公开冠县政府对他的投诉信和上级领导批示，现已超过法定期限济南司法局未公开也未回复。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对此，舒向新律师感到十分愤慨，在其微博上每日一喊。对于舒向新律师的遭遇，本网将继续予以关注。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>山东旭洲律师事务所：</span> <span>舒向新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15866637777   QQ</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1640646939</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fdsQJ9vbp_w/UFqQXOfXqfI/AAAAAAAAPEA/dftwnmUYW64/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fdsQJ9vbp_w/UFqQXOfXqfI/AAAAAAAAPEA/dftwnmUYW64/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kgJXgWLa7z8/UFqQXgtlasI/AAAAAAAAPEI/-arJqBKBNXw/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kgJXgWLa7z8/UFqQXgtlasI/AAAAAAAAPEI/-arJqBKBNXw/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7907998479011843822?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}